"```sql\nSELECT DISTINCT tags.TagName\nFROM posts\nJOIN users ON posts.OwnerUserId = users.Id\nJOIN tags ON posts.Id = tags.ExcerptPostId\nWHERE users.DisplayName = 'Mark Meckes' AND posts.CommentCount = 0;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects distinct tag names from the `tags` table for posts authored by a user with the display name \"Mark Meckes\" that have no comments. It joins the `posts`, `users`, and `tags` tables using the appropriate foreign key relationships."